00:15:04.650 --> 00:15:07.370
But there's, at the lower
level parts of the framework,

00:15:07.370 --> 00:15:11.360
this grid system helps you
deviate from those suggestions

00:15:11.360 --> 00:15:15.990
very easily and in
a very standard way.

00:15:15.990 --> 00:15:17.750
So that's one of the
things that I really

00:15:17.750 --> 00:15:18.952
loved about this process.

00:15:18.952 --> 00:15:20.660
We ended up choosing
