00:35:11.705 --> 00:35:14.080
MIKE DENNY: In general, we've
been talking about material

00:35:14.080 --> 00:35:18.220
spec and material
guidelines and how we feel

00:35:18.220 --> 00:35:21.820
they're not as
prescriptive as before.

00:35:21.820 --> 00:35:24.360
Hollow had a very
distinct personality.

00:35:24.360 --> 00:35:26.280
In the same vein,
material does, as well.

00:35:26.280 --> 00:35:29.560
And Google's products
expressing themselves

00:35:29.560 --> 00:35:34.250
using material design system
will feel very Googley.

00:35:34.250 --> 00:35:37.400
And you, and all of
