00:35:37.400 --> 00:35:41.190
be able to express their own
brands using similar elements,

00:35:41.190 --> 00:35:45.940
like sticking to the 4 or 8 DIP
grid using primary key lines.

00:35:45.940 --> 00:35:49.240
Even if you deviate
in meaningful ways,

00:35:49.240 --> 00:35:54.580
