00:37:47.890 --> 00:37:50.440
So just do make sure to test.

00:37:50.440 --> 00:37:55.070
And if you do test and
you find that there's

00:37:55.070 --> 00:38:00.060
some rendering issues, then try
to work with the original type

00:38:00.060 --> 00:38:03.750
foundry or whatever, see if
