00:38:03.750 --> 00:38:06.270
face for different use cases.

00:38:06.270 --> 00:38:08.910
In a lot of cases,
there's different variants

00:38:08.910 --> 00:38:11.990
of a type face for use
in different situations,

00:38:11.990 --> 00:38:16.407
some print design, some for
UI design, things like that.

